
'''''Rimwe na rimwe muri Mata''''' ni filime y'akozwe n'abany[[amerika]] muri 2005 ivuga kuri [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside]] yakorewe Abatutsi mu 1994 mu [[Rwanda]] <ref>When Hollywood films got the 1994 Genocide wrong - Newtimes <nowiki>https://www.newtimes.co.rw</nowiki> › section › read</ref><ref>Rwasa, Umunyarwanda wa mbere wujuje ibihumbi ijana kuri Instagram - IGIHE.com</ref>, yanditswe kandi iyobowe n'umukinnyi wa filime wo [[Hayiti|muri Hayiti]] Raoul Peck. Abakinnyi bagize itsinda barimo Idris Elba, Oris Erhuero, Carole Karemera, na Debra Winger <ref>Top 10 movies about the 1994 Genocide against the Tutsi <nowiki>https://www.newtimes.co.rw</nowiki> › lifestyle › top-10-movies...</ref><ref>Nsanzamahoro wamamaye nka 'Rwasa' muri filime yitabye ... <nowiki>https://igihe.com</nowiki> › imyidagaduro › article › nsanzamah...</ref>.

== Uko yateguwe ==
Bitandukanye na ''[[Hotel Rwanda]]'', yahawe igihembo cya PG-13 kandi ikaba yaravugaga mu buryo bwihishe inyuma ya jenoside aho kwerekana ku buryo bweruye<ref>Rwanda Film Industry Growth Impressive | IGIHE <nowiki>https://en.igihe.com</nowiki> › entertainment › rwanda-film-indu...</ref>, iyi filime yari izwiho kwerekana ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina, ryayihaye TV-MA. Byongeye kandi, amashusho atandukanye yashyizwe mu Rwanda yafatiwe muri Kigali no hafi yayo, hagaragaramo ahantu nyaburanga nka Hotel des Mille Collines ndetse na kiliziya [[Kiriziya y'umuryango mutagatifu|ya Sainte-Famille]]<ref>Sometimes in April | Africultures <nowiki>http://africultures.com</nowiki> › sometimes-in-april-5920</ref> <ref>Places of Refuge | Sometimes In April <nowiki>https://sometimesinapriljcom2010.wordpress.com</nowiki> › plac...</ref>.

Filime yabanje kwerekanwa kuri HBO . Nyuma yaje gutangazwa na PBS hanyuma isesengurwa  n’umunyamakuru jeff Greenfield hamwe na Paul Bonerwitz hamwe n’abandi<ref>Sometimes in April - Kentucky Educational Television <nowiki>https://www.ket.org</nowiki> › program › sometimes-in-april</ref> .
